definitions.definition: A human-like spiritual or immaterial being , as opposed to al-ins (people), often invisible but able to manifest in form and also inhabit people or animals; origin of the genie of Western literature, film etc.

main_definition: ( Arabic culture ) A human-like spiritual or immaterial being , as opposed to al-ins (people), often invisible but able to manifest in form and also inhabit people or animals; origin of the genie of Western literature, film etc.
